  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba9 Gas  \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Gas distribution to outlying districts has started",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Litro Company has informed that the distribution of cooking gas to the outer districts has started from today (13).",
        "He said that 3,700 metric tons of cooking gas had been brought to Sri Lanka yesterday and the work of unloading them from the ship would begin."
      ],
